text: Choa Ganj Ali Shah is a village and Union Council, an administrative subdivision, of Chakwal District in the Punjab Province of Pakistan, it is part of Chakwal Tehsil and is located at 32°49'0N 73°6'0E.Location of Chuha Ganj Ali Shah - Falling Rain Genomics ==References== Category:Union councils of Chakwal District
